Description:
As New Prestige 1 Bedroom Apartment
Desirably Situated between the Yarra River and Collins Street, embraces waterfront living with contemporary architectural innovation deigned by Koichi Takada, 889 Collins Street introduces a new era of rare waterfront living in Melbourne's evolution CBD.
This level 5 prestige 1-bedroom apartment is beautifully presented, features high quality fixtures and fittings, contemporary and sophisticated finishes thoughtful design maximizing luxury.
Residents will enjoy exclusive access to luxury Club 889 amenities including a state of the art swimming pool, gym, residents lounge and barbecue landscaped deck.
* Built in robes in bedroom
* Open plan living and dining
* Full kitchen appliances (gas cook top)
* Air conditioning and heating
* Podium landscaped exercising areas
* Indoor pool and Gym

Description:
Executive Residential Apartment in the Heart of the Melbourne CBD!
Presenting an exclusive lifestyle/investment opportunity defined by its quality, privacy and impressive space, this impeccable apartment comprises two bedrooms (both with BIRs), stylish central bathroom and a secure car space.
Stylish and secure and filled with natural lighting throughout this apartment is simply stunning roaming with panoramic views across the Yarra River and towards the Melbourne skyline. Six star facilities include access to a large outdoor poor perfect for relaxing or exercising and a state-of-the-art fitness center. Adjoining balcony connects through the spacious open plan living area and the bedroom with both of them over looking the Yarra River.
On top of all the great things things this apartment has to offer the location is unbeatable Docklands and South bank shopping, entertainment and dining are just a walk away, as are the many delights of Melbournes CBD. Plus, there are buses straight into the CBD at your door. The ideal lifestyle or perfect investment in Melbournes trendy Docklands.

Description:
Luxury Convesso One Bedroom Home Available
On offer is this superb one bedroom apartment situated in the magnificent waterfront Convesso building. Being right in the heart of Victoria Harbour, the Convesso has set the bench-mark for all future living within the Docklands precinct.
The apartment comprises of a spacious internal area of 55 sqm (approx.), with a stylish modern bathroom, designer kitchen with stainless steel appliances, stone bench tops, refrigerator and an abundance of cupboard space, a wide 9 sqm balcony perfect for entertaining or relaxing along with ducted air conditioning and heating.
In addition, the 5 star amenities in this building include 24 hour concierge, residents lounge, business centre & board room, cinema (within the Concavo building), North-facing Sky Garden facing the water with BBQ facilities, 25 metre indoor pool, spa and sauna, gymnasium and treatment room.
Great value apartment available in the First Class Convesso building and it is the perfect entry point to gain access to a luxury 5-star lifestyle.
Please call Peter Doan on 0402 959 842 for more information.
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
LARGE ONE BEDDER IN SUMPTUOUS CONVESSO
Whether an investor or first home buyer, don't miss your chance to buy into the sumptuous Convesso Complex in the Victoria Harbour Precinct - surrounded by water, parkland, cafes, bars, and restaurants, it encompasses the best of cosmopolitan Melbourne on the doorstep of the CBD.
Located on the 7th floor of this luxurious building sits this large one bed, one bath apartment, featuring an open plan living/kitchen, along with a spacious balcony with glimpses of Victoria Harbour. The chic kitchen comes with stone bench-tops, induction cook-top, and dishwasher, whilst the generous bedroom comes with mirrored built-in-robes. The bathroom has clean modern finishes, heaps of storage, and Euro-laundry. Rounding out this slick inner-city pad is central heating/cooling, and secure swipe/video intercom entry,
Designed with a premium lifestyle in mind Convesso Concavo offers its residents a 25 metre pool, spa, sauna, cinema, gym, treatment room, spacious lounge, business centre, board room, and sky garden, as well as a 24 hour concierge. With public transport on your doorstep, a resort style facilities throughout, don't miss this superb opportunity to live in sensational location.

Description:
Superb New Elm & Stone Corner Apartment
Under Offer - This stunning new light-filled corner apartment in the sophisticated Elm & Stone complex features two bedrooms with BIRs, two bathrooms, one with concealed laundry plus a generous living area with balcony and harbour glimpses.
Designed by Award-Winning Architects DKO
Enjoy an ultra-convenient lifestyle
Cutting edge interior
Exceptional owner occupier investment potential
Kitchen boasts prestige Smeg appliances & Stone benchtops
Video intercom security
R/C air conditioner
Secure basement parking
Residential storage cage
Low owners corporation fees
AMENITIES
The outstanding Elm & Stone complex offers tranquil surroundings with access to a landscaped garden with reflection pond, swimming pool, gym, rooftop deck and library with multiple study and meeting areas.
LOCATION
Enjoy a walk-to lifestyle from the heart of NewQuay and the ever improving features of the Docklands precinct including The District which features Hoyts Cinemas, Street hawker food outlets plus the soon to be opened fresh food complex The Market which will have butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket and Dan Murphys. Other attractions include easy access to the Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, leading Universities, trams (free City Circle line), Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus to Melbourne Airport

Description:
Beautiful Banksia, Inside and Out!
Superbly stylish and drenched in natural light, this stunning 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom entertainer has been expertly designed to highlight breathtaking views in contemporary comfort. Sensationally set on the 5th floor of the tightly held, often-requested Banksia building, the uninterrupted panorama overlooks Victoria Harbour, Marvel Stadium, the dazzling city skyline, and the Melbourne Wheel.
Always free-flowing, a welcoming entrance hallway takes you directly into a sleek, stone-topped kitchen fitted with high-quality Miele appliances and an integrated Fisher and Paykel fridge and freezer. The natural curves of the Banksia building frame spacious open-plan living and dining, opening up through floor-to-ceiling glass to a full-width, northeast-facing balcony. With ample space for a BBQ and a range of outdoor settings, relax, unwind and enjoy the commanding views. Showcasing breathtaking aspects from all angles, enjoy a pair of large bedrooms, complete with mirrored built-in robes and access to the roomy balcony. Both luxe bathrooms feature vibrant mosaic wall tiling, fully tiled showers and stone-finished vanities.
Take full advantage of secure parking, a concealed laundry, ducted heating and cooling throughout, video intercom entry, and this citys most spectacular lifestyle facilities including an infinity pool, plunge pools, spa, fully equipped gym and a BBQ terrace for entertaining. So close to free city circle trams, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Costco and NewQuay restaurants, this is the perfect choice for CBD professionals, downsizers and switched-on investors. Inspect with certainty!
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Prepare for superb luxury and stunning harbour views in 'Banksia'
The 'Banksia' residential complex is one of the jewels of the Docklands crown, and here is your opportunity to own a piece of it! This wonderful 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom apartment with 2 car spaces has a fantastic 5th floor position, and offers an amazing amount of style and luxury plus access to fantastic tower facilities!
Everything about this chic residence will impress including the 119 sqm (approx.) of total indoor and outdoor space! The wonderful lounge and meals zone feature a tremendous open layout and beautiful floor tiles, and has entry out to the south-facing balcony which runs all the across the apartment and produces views of Victoria Harbour that are simply spectacular.
The state-of-the-art kitchen has stunning designer touches from pendant lighting over the island bench to elegant dark cabinetry. You also get premium stainless-steel appliances. Both bedrooms each have a walk-in robe and stylish ensuite which is rare to find in Docklands apartment, as well as having direct access out to the balcony.
Other residence features include a powder room, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, and the 2 secure car spaces. You also have access to facilities including BBQs and outdoor dining, gym, sunken lounge, grand piano, kitchen, and three plunge pools with enviable views across Victoria Harbour to Melbourne's CBD.
Moments to The District Docklands with great shops, restaurants, and entertainment, sensational waterside restaurants, IGA X-Press Docklands, Ron Barassi Snr Park, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, Marvel Stadium, and trams.

Description:
Townhouse Brilliance with a Location to Cherish
With a remarkable position, this sophisticated and utterly stylish 3 bedroom + study, 2.5 bathroom residence is a class above the others.
Brilliant location aside, this gorgeous property truly sets the benchmark for townhouse living in the Docklands thanks to its superior quality and amazing attention to detail. A lower ground floor offers a private study as well as your very own garden area perfect for unwinding after a long day at work. Up a few stairs and you enter the light-filled and expansive central living zone, which has designated areas for both dining and a lounge fitted with a charming gas fireplace.
This main hub has a luxury stone kitchen right in the middle of the action, with an island bench perfect for quick meals and premium stainless steel appliances ideal for those who love to cook at home. This level also feeds out to a balcony which delivers views of the Melbourne Star Observation Wheel which is best enjoyed at night.
Three bedrooms dominate the top floor including the master bedroom which comes with a walk-in robe, generous double vanity ensuite, and a balcony. There is also a 2nd study area off one of the other bedrooms and a sleek main bathroom on the top floor. Other property extras include a powder room, laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and 2 secure car spaces.
Youll love being so close to The District Docklands with brilliant eating choices, retail outlets, and entertainment. Youre also close to IGA X-Press and Asian grocery store, waterside restaurants, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 30, 75, and 86 trams.

Description:
Unrivalled Concavo Penthouse Luxury Living with Breathtaking 270 Degree Water and City Views
Spectacularly positioned in a private and peaceful penthouse suite, this prestigious 3 bedroom 2 bathroom apartment magnificently maximises breathtaking views over Victoria Harbour, Port Phillip Bay and the stunning city skyline. Footsteps from first-class restaurants on the harbour, free city trams, Buluk Park, and Woolworths shopping, this is exceptional waterside living with all the lifestyle benefits.
Set sky-high on the top floor of the tightly held Concavo tower, the apartment sensationally opens up to reveal far-reaching living and dining behind floor-to-ceiling glass. Immerse yourself in a commanding 270 degree view, sweeping across an uninterrupted skyline touching on Port Melbourne beach, the Yarra River, both Bolte and West Gate Bridges, the Melbourne Wheel, and back towards the city rising above Marvel Stadium. Immaculately presented in display suite condition, the panorama is matched by a high-quality kitchen boasting a stone-topped island bench, chef-friendly Miele appliances including an induction cooktop, and a mirrored splashback. A sheltered, partially screened balcony places a premium on privacy with an irresistible opportunity to entertain on any scale you wish. All 3 bedrooms are large and light-filled with the palatial main showcasing dual-sided built-in robes and a luxe twin-vanity ensuite with a freestanding bath. The family bathroom comes complete with a stone-detailed vanity, doubling as a powder room.
Designed with distinction by award-winning architects Bates Smart and industry-awarded for sustainability initiatives, special features include a separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling throughout, remote-controlled roller blinds and curtains in the bedrooms, and 2 car parks plus a storage cage. The world-class resort-style facilities truly set this development apart. Enjoy a concierge, indoor lap pool, spa, sauna, fully equipped gym, private cinema, lounge with kitchenette, cinema room, business centre and boardroom, and a north-facing sky garden with a BBQ terrace and water views. This is superior waterfront living with all the penthouse luxury you deserve. Inspect with confidence!
Please call Peter Doan on 0402 959 842 for inspection details

2 CAR SPACES AVAILABLE FOR SALE AT $40,000 EACH
Definitely perfect for private investor or owner occupier!
Aquavista Tower – entry from Doepel Way, Docklands VIC 3008
The Aquavista Tower is conveniently located directly across the entry to 14 Doepel Way, Docklands VIC 3008 (NewQuay) and is adjacent to Harbour Town Shopping Centre. Lots in this location are always in demand.
There are 7 car space available in prime harbour side location, perfectly positioned within the commercial precinct specifically developed for small business.
Lot Numbers: 452 and 453
Features:
• Lockable bollards to protect space
• Access via security swipe
• Undercover Parking
• Boom Gate installed at entry
• Towing facilities available for any breach of your parking space via anytime towing
• Direct access to citylink and all major Melbourne arterial roads
• Lift access from parking space to ground floor
Please note: a congestion levy of $1410 per year, per car space, applies to non-residential car park tenants (including businesses).
No congestion levy charged for any car park tenant residing in docklands
Contact Mo Mellak at 0405 083 188 to arrange a viewing.

Description:
Lavish Yarras Edge living matched by superb city views
Everything youve been looking for in a high rise Docklands apartment is here for you with this unmissable two bedroom, two bathroom modern oasis, including sleek luxury and northern views of the stunning Yarra River and Melbourne CBD.
The kitchen will impress eager home cooks thanks to stainless steel Miele appliances, stone island bench, and excellent storage. The master bedroom has balcony access along with a double vanity ensuite and built-in robe storage. Other property features includes a concealed laundry, ducted heating and cooling throughout, secure video intercom, and 2 secure car spaces.
A 26th floor location and exceptional floorplan which allows for sensational space both inside and out are just a couple of the amazing highlights of this coveted property. The astonishing views are sure to leave you breathless, with the generous lounge and dining zone, spacious undercover balcony, and both bedrooms the best place to soak in the water and city vistas.
You also have access to an on-site gym, residence lounge and RekDek recreation centre which includes a gymnasium, indoor heated lap pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. Make the most of the Yarras Edge precinct where youre close to South Wharf Promenade which enjoys an array of bars and restaurants including The General Assembly, Meat Market, The Boatbuilders Yard, Charlie Lovett, and Munich Brauhaus. Youre also near DFO shopping, Crown Casino, and public transport including Southern Cross Station.

Incredible water views and sleek modern podium living
Set right on the edge of the picturesque marina where you have stunning uninterrupted views of the water you can enjoy 24/7, this spacious 1 bedroom apartment is blissful Yarras Edge living in the coveted Array complex.
Picturesque vistas of marina and CBD in the distance from your large balcony

Description:
Fantastic Modern Lifestyle with Amazing Bay Views
A fantastic opportunity for a showpiece modern lifestyle is now available on the 11th floor of this near new 883-889 Collins St address. This luxury 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment, located on this prestigious location right in the heart of Victoria Harbour is something you should never miss out.
With fantastic bay views on the Southern side of the South Tower, 1105S comprises spacious open plan lounge and dining zone, full glass sliding door opens to a generous sized balcony maximising the beautiful views of Port Phillip Bay. Gourmet L-shaped kitchen fully equipped with Miele appliances and stone benchtop.
Master bedroom with full ensuite and WIRs and second double bedroom opposite the main bathroom, and both complimented with the lovely Southern light, plus cupboard Euro laundry.
Extra features include polished timber floor boards, floor to ceiling windows, split system air-conditioning, intercom system, and a security car park.
You will also be spoiled by accessing the 20m swimming pool, cinema, billiards room, yoga, gym, BBQ, private dining room and resident lounge.
The new 889 Collins St Building also offers a complete range of waterfront living with prime views of Melbourne CBD and Yarra River and this exclusive address is within walking distance to Etihad Stadium, Melbourne Convention and Exhibition Centre, DFO South Wharf Shopping Mall, Crown Casino, Southern Cross Station and countless numbers of cafes, restaurants and shops, not to mention the free tram lines that will take you to Central CBD within minutes down Collins St.
Inspection By Appointment.
